BT
/F1 11 Tf
/F1 18 Tf
72 742 Td (ABSTRACT) Tj
/F1 11 Tf
72 704 Td (Raitha-Varta is a Flash-Card Advisor application for farmers. Agricultural advisories) Tj
72 689 Td (released by Krishi Vigyana Kendra and agricultural experts are often long PDF documents) Tj
72 674 Td (or lengthy text messages. Farmers may find them difficult to read and apply immediately) Tj
72 659 Td (in the field.) Tj
72 636 Td (This project converts complex crop advisory information into short Daily 1-Minute Tips.) Tj
72 621 Td (Each tip is presented as a swipeable card containing crop name, district, image, weather) Tj
72 606 Td (note, success story, Kannada guidance, and English instruction. The application also) Tj
72 591 Td (provides an Expert Ask feature where a farmer can submit crop details, problem) Tj
72 576 Td (description, and a leaf photo.) Tj
72 553 Td (A Node.js backend stores farmer requests and provides expert outcomes in Kannada and) Tj
72 538 Td (English. A browser-based Expert Dashboard allows experts to view farmer requests and) Tj
72 523 Td (update advisory replies. Room Database is used for offline viewing, Retrofit is used for) Tj
72 508 Td (API communication, ViewPager2 is used for swipe cards, and Glide is used for crop) Tj
72 493 Td (images.) Tj
ET

endstream
endobj
