BT
/F1 11 Tf
/F1 18 Tf
72 742 Td (1. PROBLEM STATEMENT) Tj
/F1 11 Tf
72 704 Td (Agricultural experts and Krishi Vigyana Kendra release crop advisories every week. These) Tj
72 689 Td (advisories are useful, but they are usually published as long PDF files or long text) Tj
72 674 Td (messages. Farmers may not have time to read detailed documents while working in the) Tj
72 659 Td (field.) Tj
72 636 Td (Farmers need short, actionable tips specific to their district, soil condition, crop) Tj
72 621 Td (type, pest situation, and weather. The main problem solved by Raitha-Varta is converting) Tj
72 606 Td (complex agricultural information into simple daily tips that farmers can understand) Tj
72 591 Td (quickly and use immediately.) Tj
ET

endstream
endobj
