BT
/F1 11 Tf
/F1 18 Tf
72 742 Td (2. DETAILED DESCRIPTION AND VISION) Tj
/F1 11 Tf
72 704 Td (Raitha-Varta is designed as a Flash-Card Advisor for farmers. It turns complex research) Tj
72 689 Td (and advisory information into Daily 1-Minute Tips. The app works like an Instagram-style) Tj
72 674 Td (swipe experience for farming, but the content is useful, advisory-based, and) Tj
72 659 Td (scientifically oriented.) Tj
72 636 Td (Each card contains one clear action. Example actions include: drain standing water for) Tj
72 621 Td (two days, remove infected leaves, inspect the stem base, apply neem cake mixture, or) Tj
72 606 Td (spray only after expert recommendation. This helps farmers avoid confusion and act) Tj
72 591 Td (quickly.) Tj
72 568 Td (The vision of this project is to make farming information digestible, local, and) Tj
72 553 Td (practical. Instead of reading long advisory documents, farmers can open the app and) Tj
72 538 Td (immediately see today?s crop tip.) Tj
ET

endstream
endobj
