BT
/F1 11 Tf
/F1 18 Tf
72 742 Td (3. APP USAGE AND USER FLOW) Tj
/F1 11 Tf
72 704 Td (Daily Tip: The farmer opens the app and instantly sees a swipeable farming tip card.) Tj
72 689 Td (Each card contains a crop image, title, crop category, district, weather note, Kannada) Tj
72 674 Td (guidance, English instruction, and success story.) Tj
72 651 Td (Crop Category: The farmer can filter tips by crop. The current project includes Paddy,) Tj
72 636 Td (Arecanut, Coconut, and Tomato categories.) Tj
72 613 Td (Success Story: Each card includes a simple local farmer success story to make the) Tj
72 598 Td (advisory relatable and motivating.) Tj
72 575 Td (Expert Ask: The farmer clicks the Expert Ask button, enters name, crop, district, and) Tj
72 560 Td (problem, chooses a diseased leaf photo, and submits it to the backend. The backend) Tj
72 545 Td (returns an expert outcome in Kannada and English.) Tj
72 522 Td (Expert Dashboard: The expert can open a browser dashboard, view submitted requests,) Tj
72 507 Td (inspect the problem details, and update Kannada and English replies.) Tj
ET

endstream
endobj
