BT
/F1 11 Tf
/F1 18 Tf
72 742 Td (5. SYSTEM ARCHITECTURE) Tj
/F1 11 Tf
72 704 Td (The system has four main parts: Android Farmer App, Room Local Database, Backend REST) Tj
72 689 Td (API, and Expert Dashboard.) Tj
72 666 Td (Android Farmer App: Displays tips, filters crops, lets farmer submit Expert Ask request,) Tj
72 651 Td (and displays expert outcome.) Tj
72 628 Td (Room Database: Stores advisory tips offline inside the device.) Tj
72 605 Td (Backend REST API: Receives requests from Android app, stores farmer problems, and) Tj
72 590 Td (returns bilingual outcomes.) Tj
72 567 Td (Expert Dashboard: Allows expert or KVK officer to review requests and update advisory) Tj
72 552 Td (replies.) Tj
72 529 Td (Architecture Flow: Farmer App -> Retrofit API Call -> Node.js Backend -> JSON Storage ->) Tj
72 514 Td (Expert Dashboard -> Kannada/English Reply -> Farmer App.) Tj
ET

endstream
endobj
