BT
/F1 11 Tf
/F1 18 Tf
72 742 Td (6. MODULES IN THE PROJECT) Tj
/F1 11 Tf
72 704 Td (1. Splash-Free Startup Module: The app directly loads the daily tip screen on startup,) Tj
72 689 Td (satisfying the requirement that the Daily Tip should load instantly.) Tj
72 666 Td (2. Flash Card Tip Module: Shows advisory information as swipeable cards using) Tj
72 651 Td (ViewPager2.) Tj
72 628 Td (3. Crop Filter Module: Allows filtering by All, Paddy, Arecanut, Coconut, and Tomato.) Tj
72 605 Td (4. Offline Storage Module: Uses Room Database with FarmTip entity, DAO, and AppDatabase) Tj
72 590 Td (classes.) Tj
72 567 Td (5. Image Loading Module: Uses Glide to load crop images from URLs.) Tj
72 544 Td (6. Expert Ask Module: Allows farmer to submit name, crop, district, problem, and leaf) Tj
72 529 Td (photo URI.) Tj
72 506 Td (7. Expert Outcome Module: Shows result in Kannada and English after backend response.) Tj
72 483 Td (8. Expert Dashboard Module: Browser page for expert to view and update responses.) Tj
ET

endstream
endobj
