BT
/F1 11 Tf
/F1 18 Tf
72 742 Td (7. BACKEND AND EXPERT DASHBOARD) Tj
/F1 11 Tf
72 704 Td (The backend is created using Node.js. It runs on port 3000 and exposes REST APIs for the) Tj
72 689 Td (Android app. The dashboard can be opened in a browser using) Tj
72 674 Td (http://127.0.0.1:3000/dashboard.) Tj
72 651 Td (Main backend endpoints are: GET /api/tips, GET /api/tips?crop=Paddy, POST /api/tips, GET) Tj
72 636 Td (/api/expert-asks, POST /api/expert-asks, POST /api/expert-asks/:id/reply, and GET) Tj
72 621 Td (/dashboard.) Tj
72 598 Td (The Expert Dashboard displays farmer name, crop, district, problem, leaf photo URI,) Tj
72 583 Td (current status, Kannada outcome, and English outcome. The expert can edit the outcome) Tj
72 568 Td (fields and save the reply.) Tj
ET

endstream
endobj
