72 742 Td (8. DATABASE DESIGN) Tj
/F1 11 Tf
72 704 Td (Android Room Table: farm_tips. Fields include id, crop, district, title, kannadaTip,) Tj
72 689 Td (englishTip, weatherNote, successStory, and imageUrl.) Tj
72 666 Td (Backend JSON Storage: expert-asks.json. Fields include id, farmerName, crop, district,) Tj
72 651 Td (problem, leafPhotoUri, status, expertAdviceKannada, expertAdviceEnglish, createdAt, and) Tj
72 636 Td (updatedAt.) Tj
72 613 Td (Room Database is used for offline tip storage, while JSON file storage is used for) Tj
72 598 Td (backend expert request persistence in the demo version.) Tj
ET

endstream
