72 742 Td (10. IMPACT GOALS) Tj
/F1 11 Tf
72 704 Td (Precision Farming: The project brings expert knowledge closer to farmers by providing) Tj
72 689 Td (crop-specific and district-specific advisory cards.) Tj
72 666 Td (Yield Improvement: By giving timely pest, disease, and crop care tips, the app can help) Tj
72 651 Td (reduce losses caused by incorrect fertilization, pest spread, and delayed action.) Tj
72 628 Td (Digital Inclusion: The project makes scientific agricultural data easier to understand) Tj
72 613 Td (by presenting it as short, simple, bilingual information.) Tj
72 590 Td (Farmer Support: The Expert Ask feature helps farmers request guidance when they see a) Tj
72 575 Td (diseased leaf or crop problem.) Tj
ET

endstream
