BT
/F1 11 Tf
/F1 18 Tf
72 742 Td (12. ADVANTAGES AND LIMITATIONS) Tj
/F1 11 Tf
72 704 Td (Advantages: Simple farmer-friendly interface, short actionable tips, crop filtering,) Tj
72 689 Td (offline support, bilingual expert outcomes, backend API support, expert dashboard, and) Tj
72 674 Td (persistent request storage.) Tj
72 651 Td (Limitations: The current leaf photo feature stores the selected image URI instead of) Tj
72 636 Td (uploading the actual image file. The expert advice is demo-based and should be verified) Tj
72 621 Td (by real agriculture experts before real-world use. The backend uses JSON storage, which) Tj
72 606 Td (is suitable for academic demonstration but not for large production systems.) Tj
72 591 Td (Authentication is not yet implemented for the dashboard.) Tj
ET

endstream
